\f0\b\fs48 \cf0 \strokec2 Overall Philosophy\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0\fs24 \cf0 Chelsea is not particularly loyal to genres.\
She is loyal to 
\f0\b how a book makes her feel.
